in my stomach for nine months,


807
00:57:18.133 --> 00:57:19.383
but I feel the same pain.

808
00:57:23.810 --> 00:57:27.930
And, you can't just take someone's life

809
00:57:27.930 --> 00:57:29.230
into your hands like that.

810
00:57:30.810 --> 00:57:32.380
This is a whole life.

811
00:57:32.380 --> 00:57:34.021
A whole destiny.

812
00:57:35.780 --> 00:57:37.130
- You don't have the right.

813
00:57:39.100 --> 00:57:42.090
Baby, we have to think about this.

814
00:57:43.698 --> 00:57:44.531
No.

815
00:57:46.615 --> 00:57:47.448
No.

816
00:57:48.687 --> 00:57:52.560
No!

817
00:57:52.560 --> 00:57:54.797
- Don't give up, baby.

818
00:57:55.931 --> 00:57:56.764
- Shh.

819
00:57:59.643 --> 00:58:00.810
Don't give up.

820
00:58:05.320 --> 00:58:06.890
- No way.

821
00:58:06.890 --> 00:58:08.223
- Come on, baby.

822
00:59:40.896 --> 00:59:41.896
- Hey, babe.

823
00:59:43.012 --> 00:59:43.845
- Hey.

824
00:59:51.870 --> 00:59:52.703
- What's wrong?

825
00:59:54.015 --> 00:59:54.848
- I'm fine.

826
00:59:57.742 --> 00:59:58.575
- Nkem!

827
01:00:01.320 --> 01:00:02.320
What have you done?!

828
01:00:08.350 --> 01:00:09.183
What's this?

829
01:00:13.363 --> 01:00:14.707
- I was going to tell you.

830
01:00:17.421 --> 01:00:18.680
- You took our baby out?!

831
01:00:21.000 --> 01:00:22.113
- I couldn't keep it.

832
01:00:23.960 --> 01:00:24.793
- It? It?!

833
01:00:26.670 --> 01:00:28.520
- Tobi.

834
01:00:28.520 --> 01:00:29.853
- How could you?

835
01:00:31.486 --> 01:00:32.319
- Tobi.

836
01:00:33.229 --> 01:00:34.062
Tobi!

837
01:00:48.999 --> 01:00:49.832
Tobi!

838
01:00:51.246 --> 01:00:52.079
Tobi.

839
01:00:53.110 --> 01:00:53.943
Wait.

840
01:00:54.846 --> 01:00:57.333
You can't possibly leave
at this time of the night.


841
01:00:59.560 --> 01:01:00.393
Tobi.

842
01:01:18.830 --> 01:01:19.663
Tobi.

843
01:01:22.610 --> 01:01:23.573
Can we talk?

844
01:01:30.740 --> 01:01:31.573
Tobi, please.

845
01:01:36.757 --> 01:01:39.424
- There's nothing to talk about.

846
01:01:40.930 --> 01:01:41.763
- Tobi.

847
01:02:03.340 --> 01:02:04.663
- Merry Christmas.

848
01:02:06.130 --> 01:02:07.107
Where have you been?

849
01:02:07.107 --> 01:02:09.260
I've been so worried.

850
01:02:09.260 --> 01:02:11.060
I thought something happened to you.

851
01:02:13.170 --> 01:02:14.253
You're drunk.

852
01:02:15.260 --> 01:02:16.443
Have you been drinking?

853
01:02:18.670 --> 01:02:19.503
- So what?

854
01:02:20.970 --> 01:02:22.173
So what if I'm drunk?

855
01:02:23.670 --> 01:02:25.790
- I can't keep doing this.

856
01:02:25.790 --> 01:02:26.710
In the last four days,

857
01:02:26.710 --> 01:02:29.610
you've been coming home
drunk every single night.


858
01:02:29.610 --> 01:02:30.883
- Just leave me alone.

859
01:02:32.960 --> 01:02:35.310
- It's high time you grow up!

860
01:02:35.310 --> 01:02:37.707
How long are you going
to continue like this?!


861
01:02:38.915 --> 01:02:41.257
You're not the only
one grieving, you know!


862
01:02:41.257 --> 01:02:43.120
Get a grip on yourself, please!

863
01:02:43.120 --> 01:02:44.143
- How dare you?

864
01:02:46.404 --> 01:02:48.554
Not everybody's as cold
hearted as you are.


865
01:02:50.260 --> 01:02:52.223
Do not make me lose my temper.

866
01:02:56.545 --> 01:02:58.220
- I'm tired.

867
01:02:58.220 --> 01:03:00.900
Can we move on already, please?

868
01:03:00.900 --> 01:03:02.333
- Look, I've held you down.

869
01:03:04.630 --> 01:03:08.843
When you cry, when you're
sad, when you're angry.


870
01:03:11.910 --> 01:03:13.190
Even when you push me away.

871
01:03:13.190 --> 01:03:14.543
I'm still right there.

872
01:03:15.910 --> 01:03:17.920
I've had to bottle up years of pain

873
01:03:17.920 --> 01:03:19.293
to make you feel good.

874
01:03:20.714 --> 01:03:21.547
And now I have
to worry about the fact

875
01:03:21.547 --> 01:03:23.243
that you don't have kids.

876
01:03:25.420 --> 01:03:27.063
I've been a good husband to you!

877
01:03:28.080 --> 01:03:29.193
Just one thing.

878
01:03:31.080 --> 01:03:34.131
Just one thing is all
I've ever asked you for,


879
01:03:34.131 --> 01:03:35.183
and you failed!

880
01:03:40.010 --> 01:03:42.653
How do you even sleep at
night after what you've done?


881
01:03:43.860 --> 01:03:46.140
You have no right to take
somebody else's life!


882
01:03:46.140 --> 01:03:47.433
You are not God!

883
01:03:52.120 --> 01:03:54.270
I can't even recognize
the woman I married.


884
01:03:57.650 --> 01:03:58.483
- So

885
01:03:59.940 --> 01:04:01.993
this is really not about the child.

886
01:04:04.270 --> 01:04:06.723
This is the satisfaction
of you being a father.


887
01:04:07.830 --> 01:04:11.060
And you don't mind being a
father, regardless of anything?


888
01:04:11.060 --> 01:04:11.893
- Yes.

889
01:04:13.330 --> 01:04:14.717
I want a child!

890
01:04:19.365 --> 01:04:20.577
It's been eight years.

891
01:04:20.577 --> 01:04:22.077
Eight years, Nkem!

892
01:04:24.091 --> 01:04:24.924
- Wow.

893
01:04:26.490 --> 01:04:30.180
What happened to if it's
between you and having children,


894
01:04:30.180 --> 01:04:31.603
you win all the time?

895
01:04:32.970 --> 01:04:35.233
I guess it was all a lie.

896
01:04:37.259 --> 01:04:39.513
I'm useless without children.

897
01:04:41.020 --> 01:04:41.853
- I guess.

898
01:04:54.119 --> 01:04:57.240
I'll be back to get my things tomorrow.

899
01:04:57.240 --> 01:04:58.413
I need some space.

900
01:06:33.310 --> 01:06:34.970
- Good morning, ma'am.

901
01:06:34.970 --> 01:06:36.553
- Good morning Akpan.

902
01:06:36.553 --> 01:06:41.553
- Forgot some enko karin
briefcase, and some a few clothes.


903
01:06:41.900 --> 01:06:43.550
- His briefcase?

904
01:06:43.550 --> 01:06:44.383
Where is he?

905
01:06:46.214 --> 01:06:47.803
- And, he said
I should give you this.

906
01:07:00.930 --> 01:07:03.740
I'm sorry, madam, please,
I'm in a hurry, ma'am.


907
01:07:03.740 --> 01:07:05.640
There's a taxi waiting for me outside.

908
01:07:07.200 --> 01:07:08.033
- Okay.

909
01:07:09.130 --> 01:07:10.380
Let me go get his things.

910
01:07:35.114 --> 01:07:36.103
- Thank you, ma'am.

911
01:07:38.450 --> 01:07:40.503
He also said that
I should give you this.

912
01:07:45.490 --> 01:07:46.650
- His car key?

913
01:07:46.650 --> 01:07:48.937
- Yes ma'am. I'll be on my way.

914
01:07:57.583 --> 01:08:00.290
- Dear Nkem, I never thought

915
01:08:00.290 --> 01:08:02.073
I would be writing you this letter.

916
01:08:03.060 --> 01:08:04.137
There was a time when I thought

917
01:08:04.137 --> 01:08:07.070
our love could stand the test of time,

918
01:08:07.070 --> 01:08:08.913
and nothing could come between us.

919
01:08:10.380 --> 01:08:13.603
To say that I've agonized over
this is an understatement.


920
01:08:15.250 --> 01:08:17.813
This situation is overwhelming for me.

921
01:08:19.010 --> 01:08:20.623
I need some time to be away.

922
01:08:23.600 --> 01:08:25.420
I'm in so much pain right now,

923
01:08:25.420 --> 01:08:29.160
that I actually dream
about a time in the future.


924
01:08:29.160 --> 01:08:30.940
When thinking about what you did

925
01:08:30.940 --> 01:08:33.633
to our unborn baby won't hurt so much.

926
01:08:35.220 --> 01:08:39.000
I still love you, and
I'll continue to love you,


927
01:08:39.000 --> 01:08:40.973
but it's tearing me apart.

928
01:08:42.430 --> 01:08:45.733
You have to let me go, so
I can find myself again.


929
01:08:47.870 --> 01:08:50.833
I left some money for you in
the drawers beside the bed.


930
01:08:51.940 --> 01:08:54.633
It should be enough to
start up a business.


931
01:08:55.964 --> 01:08:57.064
You're a strong woman.

932
01:08:57.940 --> 01:08:59.640
I know you will figure things out.

933
01:09:01.509 --> 01:09:03.210
I cherish our good memories,

934
01:09:03.210 --> 01:09:05.393
and I hope they
always stay on my mind.

935
01:09:07.260 --> 01:09:09.573
Time and distance will
help heal this wound.


936
01:09:10.960 --> 01:09:11.993
Love, always, Tobi.

937
01:09:23.668 --> 01:09:25.740
Hey! Be careful!

938
01:09:25.740 --> 01:09:29.002
Do not kick the ball
too hard at your sister!


939
01:09:31.410 --> 01:09:33.560
Can you imagine?

940
01:09:33.560 --> 01:09:35.107
Okay, that's enough!

