01:11:53.458 --> 01:11:54.291
- Hello.

942
01:11:58.860 --> 01:11:59.943
- Uncle Tobi!

943
01:12:01.553 --> 01:12:02.962
How are you doing, sir?

944
01:12:02.962 --> 01:12:04.731
- I'm very well.

945
01:12:04.731 --> 01:12:05.630
- It's been a long time.

946
01:12:05.630 --> 01:12:06.463
- How are you doing?

947
01:12:06.463 --> 01:12:07.360
- I'm good, too, sir.

948
01:12:07.360 --> 01:12:08.585
- And how's the family?

949
01:12:08.585 --> 01:12:09.948
- Everything good.

950
01:12:09.948 --> 01:12:10.781
We alright.

951
01:12:13.500 --> 01:12:14.380
How's everything, sir?

952
01:12:14.380 --> 01:12:15.620
- Fine.

953
01:12:15.620 --> 01:12:17.470
It's been about four years?

954
01:12:17.470 --> 01:12:18.303
- Yes, sir.

955
01:12:19.340 --> 01:12:20.863
- So how is the whole family?

956
01:12:20.863 --> 01:12:23.224
- We've been good, everybody's fine.

957
01:12:23.224 --> 01:12:24.853
- That's great.

958
01:12:26.550 --> 01:12:29.853
I just came to check for Nkem,
it seems she's not around?


959
01:12:31.553 --> 01:12:32.783
- Ah, hey, uncle Tobi,

960
01:12:32.783 --> 01:12:36.023
aunt Nkem left here like
four years ago, sir.


961
01:12:37.190 --> 01:12:38.103
Are you not aware?

962
01:12:39.190 --> 01:12:41.293
Don't you come to get with your wife?

963
01:12:42.550 --> 01:12:46.793
She told my mother that
you traveled out for work.


964
01:12:49.000 --> 01:12:50.603
- I did, yes, I did.

965
01:12:54.190 --> 01:12:55.580
Okay.

966
01:12:55.580 --> 01:12:56.413
Thank you.

967
01:12:56.413 --> 01:12:57.290
- Yes, sir.

968
01:12:58.687 --> 01:13:00.950
Uncle Tobi, wait.

969
01:13:00.950 --> 01:13:04.130
Sir, the last time my mother saw her,

970
01:13:04.130 --> 01:13:08.083
she say she now owns
an hair salon business.


971
01:13:09.850 --> 01:13:11.830
She even give her her address.

972
01:13:11.830 --> 01:13:13.510
Can I get it for you, sir?

973
01:13:13.510 --> 01:13:14.343
- Yes.

974
01:13:14.343 --> 01:13:15.176
Yes, please.

975
01:13:15.176 --> 01:13:16.023
- Okay, I get it for you.

976
01:13:16.023 --> 01:13:17.856
Wait here, uncle Tobi.

977
01:13:19.011 --> 01:13:20.011
- Thank you.

978
01:14:39.259 --> 01:14:40.220
- You're still so beautiful.

979
01:14:40.220 --> 01:14:42.010
You haven't aged a day.

980
01:14:45.080 --> 01:14:46.333
- Tobi, what do you want?

981
01:14:51.140 --> 01:14:52.150
- I just...

982
01:14:54.980 --> 01:14:56.873
- He comes back after four years,

983
01:14:58.349 --> 01:15:02.022
and the first thing he does
is try to use his charm on me?


984
01:15:02.022 --> 01:15:03.790
I didn't-
- It's not like-


985
01:15:03.790 --> 01:15:06.140
- I need to refresh, now,
how did we even meet?


986
01:15:07.550 --> 01:15:08.383
- Look, I-

987
01:15:09.350 --> 01:15:10.655
- Nevermind.

988
01:15:10.655 --> 01:15:12.173
It's your specialty.

989
01:15:14.460 --> 01:15:15.360
- Look, I'm sorry.

990
01:15:17.054 --> 01:15:20.095
I'm sorry.
- Sorry for what, exactly?


991
01:15:20.095 --> 01:15:22.033
- Look, it wasn't exactly easy for me.

992
01:15:23.070 --> 01:15:24.423
- And it was easy for me?

993
01:15:31.160 --> 01:15:34.330
- Look, the death of our child

