997
01:15:44.055 --> 01:15:45.350
I killed him.

998
01:15:45.350 --> 01:15:46.183
- Stop.

999
01:15:47.080 --> 01:15:48.210
Stop talking like that.

1000
01:15:48.210 --> 01:15:52.430
- Where have you been all these years?

1001
01:15:52.430 --> 01:15:53.570
You come back here,

1002
01:15:53.570 --> 01:15:55.290
and you tell me sorry?

1003
01:15:55.290 --> 01:15:57.253
Sorry doesn't cut it, Tobi.

1004
01:15:58.330 --> 01:15:59.470
- Look, all this time,

1005
01:15:59.470 --> 01:16:00.990
I've just been trying to numb the pain

1006
01:16:00.990 --> 01:16:02.390
of everything that happened.

1007
01:16:04.910 --> 01:16:05.910
Even thinking of it,

1008
01:16:05.910 --> 01:16:07.460
even thinking of what happened.

1009
01:16:11.130 --> 01:16:13.880
I wouldn't have survived all those years.

1010
01:16:13.880 --> 01:16:15.270
I just needed to get away.

1011
01:16:15.270 --> 01:16:16.233
I needed to heal.

1012
01:16:17.630 --> 01:16:20.180
I didn't want to come back
here a shattered person.


1013
01:16:21.770 --> 01:16:23.333
- Do you hear yourself?

1014
01:16:24.458 --> 01:16:26.373
He was my child, too!

1015
01:16:28.290 --> 01:16:29.903
I mourned his death!

1016
01:16:31.340 --> 01:16:33.540
How do you think I
survived all these years?


1017
01:16:43.240 --> 01:16:45.900
- Yes, I know I'm mean,

1018
01:16:45.900 --> 01:16:48.500
and yes, I am selfish,

1019
01:16:48.500 --> 01:16:49.333
and I'm me.

1020
01:16:50.461 --> 01:16:52.700
But, there's nothing else I can say,

1021
01:16:52.700 --> 01:16:54.313
but I'm sorry.

1022
01:16:56.680 --> 01:16:57.513
- Sorry?

1023
01:17:01.180 --> 01:17:02.540
Okay, Tobi, wait, wait.

1024
01:17:02.540 --> 01:17:05.303
Wait, first, where have
you been all these years?


1025
01:17:06.580 --> 01:17:07.580
- What does that matter?

1026
01:17:07.580 --> 01:17:09.150
- I need to know!

1027
01:17:12.690 --> 01:17:14.332
- Look, I just
needed to get some solace.

1028
01:17:14.332 --> 01:17:16.890
- Where did you go?!

1029
01:17:16.890 --> 01:17:18.627
- I had to go back to London.

1030
01:17:19.690 --> 01:17:20.523
- Wow.

1031
01:17:22.980 --> 01:17:24.890
How convenient.

1032
01:17:24.890 --> 01:17:25.963
- Convenient?

1033
01:17:27.910 --> 01:17:31.197
Look, it wasn't as easy as you think.

1034
01:17:31.197 --> 01:17:32.540
- Hmph.

1035
01:17:32.540 --> 01:17:34.780
- I got into depression.

1036
01:17:34.780 --> 01:17:37.413
I was becoming a shadow of myself.

1037
01:17:39.640 --> 01:17:42.153
I didn't want to come back
here a shattered person.


1038
01:17:46.898 --> 01:17:48.148
- You are mean!

1039
01:17:49.397 --> 01:17:51.103
You are wicked, Tobi!

1040
01:17:52.070 --> 01:17:54.020
You're so heartless!

1041
01:17:54.020 --> 01:17:56.533
- No, no, come on-
- You are heartless!


1042
01:17:56.533 --> 01:17:57.415
- Please, I'm sorry.

1043
01:17:57.415 --> 01:18:00.215
I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

1044
01:18:00.215 --> 01:18:02.110
Please, please find a way to-

1045
01:18:02.110 --> 01:18:03.402
- You're so wicked!

1046
01:18:03.402 --> 01:18:04.336
So wicked!

1047
01:18:16.970 --> 01:18:19.147
- Just accept my apology.

1048
01:18:19.147 --> 01:18:21.994
Accept my apology, please.

1049
01:18:21.994 --> 01:18:22.827
Please.

1050
01:18:31.639 --> 01:18:34.593
- Don't come back here again.

1051
01:18:35.860 --> 01:18:37.643
I don't want to ever see you.

1052
01:18:41.770 --> 01:18:42.603
- That's too much.

1053
01:18:42.603 --> 01:18:43.436
Nkem!

1054
01:19:10.325 --> 01:19:11.408
- Be careful!

1055
01:19:12.276 --> 01:19:16.998
Do not kick the ball so hard
at your sister!


1056
01:19:16.998 --> 01:19:21.998
- Okay, pass it to me! 
Pass it to me!

1057
01:19:29.283 --> 01:19:30.116
- Tobi?

1058
01:19:31.127 --> 01:19:32.222
Tobi.

1059
01:19:32.222 --> 01:19:33.680
Tobi!

1060
01:19:33.680 --> 01:19:34.513
Tobi!

1061
01:19:36.412 --> 01:19:38.515
Tobi, no!

1062
01:19:38.515 --> 01:19:39.348
No, Tobi.

1063
01:19:48.879 --> 01:19:49.796
Tobi!

1064
01:20:03.919 --> 01:20:04.752
- Tobi?

1065
01:20:17.757 --> 01:20:18.783
- I'm sorry.

1066
01:20:21.420 --> 01:20:22.253
I'm sorry.

1067
01:20:23.666 --> 01:20:24.499
I'm sorry.

1068
01:20:25.373 --> 01:20:30.373
- I know.

1069
01:20:59.270 --> 01:21:00.370
- Mama, are you ready?

1070
01:21:05.370 --> 01:21:06.570
I'll give you some time.

1071
01:21:08.140 --> 01:21:10.880
I found this in dad's wardrobe.

1072
01:21:10.880 --> 01:21:11.713
Here.

1073
01:21:19.699 --> 01:21:22.032
We'll be waiting in the car.

1074
01:21:31.074 --> 01:21:33.350
- Dear Nkem,

1075
01:21:33.350 --> 01:21:34.750
I woke up this morning

1076
01:21:34.750 --> 01:21:36.943
remembering almost everything.

